**Authorization code**

- Under Domain name >> Click on the domain name you want to send authorization code.
- 
- Click on the "Action" tab >> then click on Auth Code Button. The authorization code will send to the domain contact email address

**Send OpenSRS login Details**

- Under Domain name >> Click on the domain name you want to send OpenSrs login details.
- 
- Click on the "Action" tab >> then click on Password Button --> Resend Password. The system will send the password reset link to the domain contact email address. Find the reset link and set new password.
